appeared on Earth
before life itself.

40
00:02:28.208 --> 00:02:30.250
We don't know what
mysterious stellar wisdom

41
00:02:30.292 --> 00:02:32.416
created them and left them here,

42
00:02:32.458 --> 00:02:34.750
but we received this gift

43
