for terraforming.

51
00:03:02.667 --> 00:03:04.250
<i>The unmanned vehicle</i>

52
00:03:04.833 --> 00:03:07.167
<i>completed a "jump"
to the solar system TESS</i>

53
00:03:07.750 --> 00:03:09.916
