stuff like this.

92
00:08:36.875 --> 00:08:38.500
This isn't about speculation.

93
00:08:38.750 --> 00:08:39.958
It's a theory.

94
00:08:41.417 --> 00:08:44.042
Maybe it was
a lost civilization.

95
00:08:44.500 --> 00:08:45.875
We know from experience

96
